  "created_at": "2016-12-20T14:02:46Z",
  "updated_at": "2017-03-01T06:34:21Z",
  "closed_at": null,
  "body": "**环境：** Chrome@55.0\r\n**依赖：** Weex-toolkit@0.6.4\r\n**问题：** 在横向布局下利用 animation.transition.transform 进行横向位移动画，当移动至图片所在区域时图片不会被动态载入。\r\n\r\n> image elements which have attribute 'i-lazy-src' were elements\r\n   that had been preprocessed by lib-img-core, but not loaded yet, and\r\n   must be loaded when 'appear' events were fired. It turns out the\r\n   'appear' event was not fired correctly in the css-translate-transition\r\n   situation, so 'i-lazy-src' must be checked and lazyload must be\r\n   fired manually.\r\n\r\n在 global lib 中找到这样一段注释，请问在 weex 中应该如何手动 fire 图片加载。\r\n\r\n另外，在 `<scroller>` 组件中由于无法解决该问题 ，直接对图片进行了 preload。[注释](https://github.com/alibaba/weex/blob/6f58f89c9ec9a6962bfea0b1008b5bb1ddc3f64a/html5/render/browser/extend/components/slider/index.js#L191)\r\n\r\n如果可以对 `<image>` 添加 `data-lazy='false'` 的属性在 `lazyimg` 中强制加载图片避免懒加载的问题，但是 hyphenated 语法会自动将该属性转成 `datalazy='false'`。",
  "closed_by": null
